@startuml
skinparam sequenceDiagram

participant User as "User"
participant libdrift as "libdrift"
participant Advertisement channel as "Advertisement channel"
participant Control channel as "Control channel"
participant driftd as "driftd"
participant Neo4j as "Neo4j"
participant MongoDB as "MongoDB"

note over User, libdrift
  Retrieval message contains<br/>index specifier<br/>index value
end note

User ->> libdrift: get Part value
libdrift ->> User: ACK

libdrift ->> Advertisement channel: send retrieval message
Advertisement channel ->> driftd: get Part value
driftd ->> Neo4j: Lookup Part UUID in index
driftd ->> Neo4j: Get Part info

alt [Composite Part]
  loop [foreach Part]
    driftd ->> Neo4j: Get Part metadata with UUID
    Neo4j ->> driftd: Get Part values
  end
end

alt [Simple Part]
  driftd ->> Neo4j: Get Part metadata with UUID
  Neo4j ->> driftd: Get Part values
end

driftd ->> Advertisement channel: Update messages for Part values
Advertisement channel ->> User: receive update message

driftd ->> Neo4j: build update message
Neo4j ->> driftd: (white ovals)
driftd ->> Neo4j: (white ovals)
